title: Balenciaga Unveils New Water-Resistant Boxy Wind Jackets
text:
Visit the original post to see all 6 images from this gallery. 
Didnâ€™t get the exact outerwear you were hoping for over the holidays? Then you may want to check out these new wind jackets that Balenciaga is releasing next month.
Optioned in black as well as red, the outerwear boasts a water-resistant finish, an adjustable hood under the collar, concealed zip closure, mesh lining, and graphic Balenciaga branding on the chest and back.
To go ahead and lock in your size, you can pre-order the jackets ($830 USD) today online . Shipping begins February 15.
